{"title":"校门外的树 2","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2916","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>校门外有N棵树，每天都有一位同学给编号Ai到B的树浇水Li升。就这样，过了M天。</p>\n<p>M天后，小明捡到了一瓶药水，可以浇连续K棵树，使浇的树结果（每升水可以结一个果子）。</p>\n<p>求小明最多能收获多少个果子。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N M K</p>\n<p>M行，Ai，Bi，Li。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>最多果子数</p>\n<p>第1个结点值</p>\n<p>第2个结点值</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4 2 3</p>\n<p>1 2 2</p>\n<p>2 4 3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>11</p>\n<p>0</p>\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N&lt;=20（数据很小，所以<strong>必须输出线段树的前2个结点的值</strong>）。</p>\n<p>(若不存在，输出-1）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}